									<p>The conference will be held in the Ogden Centre West building, recently completed in October 2016.
										This is on the Durham University Science site next to the main Physics Department.<br>
									The nearest airport is Newcastle Airport (about 40min-1hr by taxi) and the nearest train
									station is in Durham City centre (25 min walk or a 5 min taxi ride).</p>
									<p>For more information, see the <a href="http://astro.dur.ac.uk/CEA/index.php?content=Contacts/Zoom">Physics Department guide</a>.</p>
